:{},"article":{}},{"id":"a4d6dcef63","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：介绍一下吧，你们哪几个是主要负责的？","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"de5ca9eee2","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们有没有团委呀？","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"734fe6b4ff","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：没有，我们只有联络员。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e85138e636","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报丁莱夫的“七 · 二九”黑报告，当谈到丁莱夫说群众批评他是“鸡蛋里头挑骨头” 时）","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"50bd2de929","type":"paragraph","text":"张：这是谁说的？丁莱夫？","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8568fd6008","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：对。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fecf86682d","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报丁莱夫搞假选举阴谋）","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c96bbd7262","type":"paragraph","text":"张：那你们局里现在还没有选举文革委员会？","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c32bca55e","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：没有，还是旧文革领导。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b4a36fc70c","type":"paragraph","text":"张：是指定的，还是选举的？","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"166aa509a6","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：选举的，但实际上是指定的，基本上是局党委和各大口负责人。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ba8bc8da93","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报丁莱夫在广播学院事件上，对抗中央文革的罪行。谈到丁说“不能说一千二百人都是右派”时）","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"325fc508ee","type":"paragraph","text":"张：那时特别对一千二百人讲了话，说你们是受蒙蔽的，包