"id":"578dd10e94","type":"paragraph","text":"张：他真有本领吗？技术上怎么样？","index":46,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5918a3ab13","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：×××人。","index":73,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5b126010b5","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：就这样吧，你们说，我们听。","index":3,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5c2f94e665","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：大概第六次。","index":61,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6af9173408","type":"paragraph","text":"〖按：一九六六年十月十八日，《毛泽东思想战斗团》从资产阶级反动路线的白色恐怖中冲杀出来，大造梅益、丁莱夫等一小撮走资派的反。丁莱夫为了维持梅丁王朝的反动统治，扑灭革命的烈火，操纵《誓死纵队》和《红色造反团》，围剿革命派。在我们斗争最艰苦，最激烈的时刻，十二月十一日下午，毛主席司令部派张春桥、姚文元同志来我局，接见了《毛泽东思想战斗团》的十五名代表。张春桥、姚文元同志和代表们亲切交谈了三个多小时，对《毛泽东思想战斗团》的革命行动表示支持。下面是这次接见的谈话纪要。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6df487777d","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：可以想一想这个问题嘛！","index":87,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"723ee932f3","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报局文革迫害鲁迅的儿子周海婴。当谈到有人问周海婴去南方干什么时）","index":19,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7599940ccf","type":"paragraph","text":"张：多久的时间？","index":55,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"786b8899c0","type":"paragraph","text":"张：政治部有多少人？你们战斗团占多少？","index":75,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d8ce1cbda","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报有一次毛主席接见红卫兵时，电视中出现丁莱夫，《誓死纵队》一些队员欢呼）","index":59,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7ddd5a29c2","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们有没有团委呀？","index":6,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"7a100171c2","publicat